    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tangy TD: Hero Tower Defense, Class Based,</strong> <strong>Roguelite, Item Combining</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic tower defense where enemies fight back! Play heroine Tangy, move towers, attack &amp; unlock roguelite upgrades! Place class-based Towers (Defender, Archer, Healer) Equip them with items for new abilities. Combine them to create powerful builds. Supported by an extensive Skilltree.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Equip and Combine over 100 different items.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/00fa021f74b0a12b3060aa6ac4c04a04.poster.avif?t=1772205339\" width=1170 height=674 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/00fa021f74b0a12b3060aa6ac4c04a04.webm?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/00fa021f74b0a12b3060aa6ac4c04a04.mp4?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M<strong>ove around Towers,</strong> Fight Big Bosses!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/97cf2d7fdf2c108f85ec7007c22ac833.poster.avif?t=1772205339\" width=1170 height=604 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/97cf2d7fdf2c108f85ec7007c22ac833.webm?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/97cf2d7fdf2c108f85ec7007c22ac833.mp4?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spend Skillpoints</strong> earned by defeating enemies in a <strong>giant Skilltree</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/3cb152b0cf52cfdc0876792241e99362.poster.avif?t=1772205339\" width=1170 height=674 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/3cb152b0cf52cfdc0876792241e99362.webm?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2245620/extras/3cb152b0cf52cfdc0876792241e99362.mp4?t=1772205339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three classes with unique skill sets. Defender, Archer and Healer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Skill Tree for each class to progress through and grow more powerful.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless Mode. Test your strategy against waves of enemies that become exponentially more difficult.</p></li></ul>",
